<div>
    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:13.5pt">您好 親愛的夥腿</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">近日多位粉絲反應接到冒充夥伴玩具的電話，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:black"><br></span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">如有下列幾點狀況，皆非夥伴通知來電，</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:black">*</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">告知系統錯誤，升級成高級會員，需加收會員費</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:black"><br></span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">→</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:red">夥伴沒有會員分級制度，這是詐騙！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif"><br><span style="color:black">*</span></span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">告知成為經銷商，需支付多餘的下單數量金額</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:black"><br></span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">→</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:red">夥伴不會將官網顧客判定為經銷</span><span style="font-size:18.0pt;color:red">，這是詐騙！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:black">*</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">因系統錯誤要寄送補償優惠券，並向您確認收件資料</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:black"><br></span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">→</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:red">夥伴目前無任何優惠劵活動</span><span style="font-size:18.0pt;color:red">，這是詐騙！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:black">*</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">詢問商品滿意度</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt">→</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:red">夥伴目前無任何滿意度調查</span><span style="font-size:18.0pt;color:red">，這是詐騙！</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:black">------------------------------<wbr>------------</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">以上皆為</span><span style="font-size:24.0pt;color:black">詐騙假冒</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">，煩請夥腿們，</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">如有接到疑似詐騙電話，千萬</span><span style="font-size:24.0pt;color:red">不要</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">「<u>提供帳戶資料</u>」以及「<u>操作任何<wbr>轉帳動作</u>」，</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">務必掛掉並撥打</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:13.5pt;font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:black">165</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">反詐騙專線諮詢、檢舉或報案，</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:18.0pt;color:black">此次在夥腿們反映第一時間，<wbr>已主動協請工程師檢查狀況並加強後台維護，</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:18.0pt;color:black">也請夥腿放心，因為賣場付款金流皆經由綠界系統，<wbr>官網無任何帳戶及信用卡個資。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:18.0pt;color:black">造成困擾深感抱歉，我們已在積極處裡當中，</span><span style="font-size:13.5pt;color:black">煩請多多包涵，</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size:18.0pt;color:black">也感謝各位夥腿的支持，後續如有任何問題盡快與我們聯繫，<wbr>將會於第一時間提供協助。</span><span lang="EN-US"></span></p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
    </div>
